    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;h2 id="dft-business-plan-input-indicator"&gt;DfT Business Plan input indicator&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3 id="geographical-coverage-england"&gt;Geographical coverage: England&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h3 id="information-broken-down-by-region---data-are-available-for-london-english-metropolitan-areas-as-a-group-and-english-non-metropolitan-areas-as-a-group"&gt;Information broken down by: Region - data are available for London, English metropolitan areas (as a group), and English non-metropolitan areas (as a group)&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h2 id="latest-data"&gt;Latest data&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In 2011/12, the average level of subsidy (direct from central government) per passenger journey was 9.2 pence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="table-for-net-government-support-for-local-bus-services-and-concessionary-travel-per-passenger-journey-by-metropolitan-area-status-england-annual-from-200405"&gt;Table for Net government support for local bus services and concessionary travel per passenger journey by metropolitan area status: England, annual from 2004/05&lt;/h2&gt;

