    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/port-marine-safety-code"/>
    <title>Port marine safety code</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary>Safety code for harbour authorities with statutory powers and duties in the UK.</summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The ‘Port marine safety code’ establishes a national standard for every aspect of port marine safety and aims to enhance safety for those who use or work in ports, their ships, passengers and the environment. The code applies to all harbour authorities in the UK that have statutory powers and duties.&lt;/p&gt;

